WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.449
People were wondering about prayer cues and things like that.

00:00:04.449 --> 00:00:07.140
They want to know some more things, so I'm going to give you a couple right here.

00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:15.673
Okay, in Ephesians it talks about how we wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities and powers, and there's a lot more to the verse.

00:00:15.673 --> 00:00:17.819
But for time's sake, there you go.

00:00:17.819 --> 00:00:22.100
It's Ephesians 4:16, I believe, somewhere around there.

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:26.400
You cannot pray against somebody's will.

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:31.845
Okay, like say you go to work and your boss is really mean to you.

00:00:31.845 --> 00:00:39.828
Maybe you're a teenager right now and you're watching me, and you are in a verbally abusive relationship with your parents.

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:50.753
When you are being assaulted like that, it is a demonic presence behind it, and so you take authority over the devil.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:52.750
This is how I would do it.

00:00:52.750 --> 00:00:57.690
I had a boss that was not very nice to me, and he treated me pretty poorly.

00:00:57.690 --> 00:01:12.435
So every day I would drive to work and say, 'I bind the maneuvering of any demonic spirits in so-and-so, and you will not torment me in any way today at all.

00:01:12.435 --> 00:01:20.420
I take authority over the spirits that maneuver inside of him, and I command them to stop right now.

00:01:20.420 --> 00:01:31.460
You have no right, no power, no authority, and I bind you up, and you are not able to maneuver and torment in any way in the name of Jesus.

00:01:31.460 --> 00:01:37.500
' Concerning abuse, I bind the devils that are tormenting my husband or my wife.

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:40.902
I bind that devil in the name of Jesus.

00:01:40.902 --> 00:01:47.440
I command you to cease and desist in your maneuvering, and I command you to stop it right now.

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:51.703
You will not maneuver in them anymore.

00:01:51.703 --> 00:02:00.824
I command you to stop this, and I call peace to the spouse, or whoever, in the name of Jesus.

00:02:00.824 --> 00:02:04.533
I call peace over them, and that's how I pray.

00:02:04.533 --> 00:02:06.103
I don't bind them.

00:02:06.103 --> 00:02:09.884
You can't bind them because they have free will, okay?

00:02:09.884 --> 00:02:14.811
And you get into some kind of witchcraft sometimes when you start doing that, praying over their emotions.

00:02:14.811 --> 00:02:19.200
