00:02:33.435 --> 00:02:40.477
Father, I thank you that my product is desirable, that people want what I'm selling.

00:02:40.477 --> 00:02:47.134
I thank you, Father, that I am blessed in the city and the field, coming in and going out, according to Deuteronomy 28.

00:02:47.134 --> 00:02:57.735
