00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:05.540
You don't manipulate people in the spirit realm.

00:03:05.540 --> 00:03:07.346
It's part of witchcraft, okay?

00:03:07.346 --> 00:03:08.717
You don't do that.

00:03:08.717 --> 00:03:10.185
