Father, I thank you, Lord, it may be an angel that they don't even know, an angel unaware.

00:05:36.368 --> 00:05:44.790
It could be a hitchhiker, I don't know whoever, that finally walks up to him and says boom, and the power of God moves on him in a supernatural way.

00:05:44.790 --> 00:05:56.460
