Okay, He's already done it all, folks.

00:06:01.037 --> 00:06:02.665
He's already done it all.

00:06:02.665 --> 00:06:05.340
He's already done everything He can do for your healing.

00:06:05.340 --> 00:06:09.120
You've got to stay in agreement with what He's already done in His Word.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:12.990
First Peter 2:24, 'By His stripes we are healed.

